title: Post production work of 'Yadav Paan Bhandar' completed
text:
The post production work of Manoj Tiwari's 'Yadav Paan Bhandar' has recently been completed. Manoj Tiwari will be seen with Gunjan Pant in the film. The film has been produced by Jeetesh Dubey and promises to be a full on entertainer. Film is directed by Ajay Kumar.
Sanjay Pandey, Brijesh Triptahi, Seema Singh are the other stars in the movie.
